  Senior Data Engineer - San Diego, CA


   SmartDrive Systems, Inc.



   What You'll Do


   Devise methods for identifying data patterns and trends in available information sources to produce financial and market intelligence. Duties include:


   develop and design data processing engines and programs to support big data platforms;


Analyze, model, transform, and visualize datasets for online products and Backend data platforms;
Implement data engineering codebase;
Design and develop data solutions for fast data stores, warehousing,
Machine learning and computer vision analytics; and
Build data pipelines and micro-service based architecture across products.



   In connection with the above duties, apply theoretical knowledge and/or skills of:


Process big data stored in distributed file systems such as Hadoop file systems (HDFS) and Hbase;
