Writing script using Python;
Spring Framework;
Distributed Systems.



   What You'll Bring:


Qualifications:


   Master’s degree in Computer Science , Information Technology, Computer Information Systems, Computer Engineering, Electrical Engineering, Engineering, or foreign equivalent.



   One (1) year of experience in job offered or alternate occupations (at all levels) of: Software Engineer; Tech Lead; Software Developer; Project Engineer; System Analyst; or Programmer Analyst.



